                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一个逆袭的小屌丝跟绿茶婊的故事~</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="388431848">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-388431848" class="vote-count">0</span>
